info.description: Place colored, shaped blocks into playing area to connect as many pieces as possible to earn points and block opponents. Highest score wins.
info.helpText: Players take seats. Click die at top of screen to choose random piece to play. Place piece on board. Press next icon button to indicate turn is over.
